                    <span>This book is a real asset to any business manager - a must read- easy to follow - great tips for sound management.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Real Must for Effective Managers Today</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
